trans-unit.source: Use the `AssignCulture` element in your project file to create and execute this task.
trans-unit.target: 使用`AssignCulture`项目文件以创建和执行此任务中的元素。

trans-unit.source: For usage and parameter information, see [AssignCulture Task](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关用法和参数信息，请参阅[AssignCulture 任务](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture"></xref> class.
Gets a list of <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files*> with a `Culture` metadata entry added to each item.
trans-unit.target: 获取一份<xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files*>与`Culture`元数据条目添加到每个项。</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files*>

trans-unit.source: If the incoming item from the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files%2A> property already contains a `Culture` metadata entry, the original metadata entry is used.
trans-unit.target: 如果传入的项从<xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files%2A>属性已包含`Culture`使用元数据条目，原始的元数据条目。</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files%2A>

trans-unit.source: The task only assigns a `Culture` metadata entry if the file name contains a valid culture identifier.
trans-unit.target: 任务仅分配`Culture`元数据条目的文件名称包含有效的区域性标识符。

trans-unit.source: The culture identifier must be between the last two dots in the filename.
trans-unit.target: 区域性标识符必须在文件名中的最后两个点之间。

trans-unit.source: The list of <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files*>, with a `Culture` metadata entry added to each item.
trans-unit.target: 列表<xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files*>，与`Culture`元数据条目添加到每个项。</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.Files*>

trans-unit.source: Gets a subset of <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.AssignedFiles*> that have a `Culture` metadata entry.
trans-unit.target: 获取的子集<xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.AssignedFiles*>具有`Culture`元数据条目。</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.AssignedFiles*>

trans-unit.source: A subset of <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.AssignedFiles*> that have a `Culture` metadata entry.
Gets a subset of <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.AssignedFiles*> that do not have a `Culture` metadata entry.
trans-unit.target: 获取的子集<xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.AssignedFiles*>不具有`Culture`元数据条目。</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.AssignedFiles*>

trans-unit.source: A subset of <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.AssignedFiles*> that do not have a `Culture` metadata entry.
Gets a subset of <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.AssignedFiles*> that do not have a `Culture` metadata entry.
trans-unit.target: 获取的子集<xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.AssignedFiles*>不具有`Culture`元数据条目。</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.AssignedFiles*>

trans-unit.source: A subset of <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.AssignCulture.AssignedFiles*> that do not have a `Culture` metadata entry.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if task execution succeeded; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果任务成功执行;否则为<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a list of files with embedded culture names to assign a culture to.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置与要为其分配区域性的嵌入的区域性名称的文件的列表。

trans-unit.source: The list of files with embedded culture names to assign a culture to.
trans-unit.target: 具有要为其分配区域性的嵌入的区域性名称的文件的列表。
